Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:51.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:54.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是森林的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:59.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,是为了守护森林  让其存续的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:02.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,巡视森林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:08.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,观察植物  动物等一切生物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:11.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,不干涉食物链
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:16.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,仅仅管理着自然之理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:22.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,森林是诞生生命  哺育生命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:26.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,并且是其最终回归大地的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:29.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,森林有着其法则
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:35.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,我作为其法则的纽带  在森林里度过了千年的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:37.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,时机一到便回归森林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:43.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,我未曾怀疑过这是我的存在意义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,直到那个时候为止…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:13.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,人类的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸…爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:28.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,她称我为「父亲」
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,----op----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:42.83,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何なんだろう　この胸のモヤモヤは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:42.83,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}心中的这份躁动  是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:50.59,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}洗いたてのタオルに顔を埋めるような
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:50.59,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}就像将脸埋入刚洗过的毛巾一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:57.72,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥が鳴いている　朝焼けのメロディー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:57.72,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鸟儿们吟唱着  朝霞的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:08.78,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どこまで歩いても　この道は続いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:08.78,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}无论走到哪  这道路都会延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:17.88,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手を繋ぐよりも　指を繋ぐような
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:17.88,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比起手牵手  更像是紧握这手指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:24.65,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒い夜は寄り添い合って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:24.65,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒冷的夜晚彼此相依
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:30.01,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}星空の毛布で眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:30.01,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}以星空为毯子安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:35.25,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}テーブルの向こうの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:35.25,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}餐桌对面的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:43.69,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}最果ての地を君と目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:43.69,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}为你指向尽头之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:53.20,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}ありがとうはこっちの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:53.20,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我才该说谢谢你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:09.01,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,800)\blur5\pos(1618.8,1043.6)}旅行的父女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:14.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:15.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,给我站住  兔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.50,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:35.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,感谢你带路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.29,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,喂  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在这里啊  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:47.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,我应该告诉过你不要擅自消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,听我说  虽然我让蝴蝶逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过我发现了兔子就去追…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,在旅行中散开会有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要离开我目所能及的范围
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:02.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,那要看时间和场合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,城镇  能看到城镇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,来啊  欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,之前真是多谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:25.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,不不  不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,你好  之前承您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,走了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:35.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,这个城镇好大啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:39.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,应该是至今为止拜访的城镇里最繁荣的一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:41.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,与此相应的危险也会增加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,需要小心谨慎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:45.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,喂  猫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:47.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,come  on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:48.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃饭！吃饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,今日的推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,灯笼鱼包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:15.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,这是饱含必要营养的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:16.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要吃剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:28.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:29.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸也尝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:32.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:36.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆只要有氧气  阳光以及水就能活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:38.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:41.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,客人您是哥雷姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:42.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,这可真是少见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,我可是第一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆还真是吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:52.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,我还以为你们只呆在森林里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,而且还带着孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,那个孩子是什么种族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:59.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,属于「牛角族」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:03.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,真的诶  长着一对可爱的角呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,话说回来  两位旅客为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:09.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们在找寻人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:10.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:15.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们是为了找到人类  才踏上的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:20.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过你们有见到人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:25.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,说的也是  不久前市场上不就有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:29.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,人类吗  那可真是很美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,我还想再吃一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:36.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过为什么人类消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,这是很久很久以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:47.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们和人类在彼此不知道的相隔甚远的土地生存着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:53.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,就在这时  一位人类找到了我们的住所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,两个种族相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:59.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,尽管相互震惊  不过接下来消除戒心后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,两个种族就交流了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:09.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过  人类将我们称之为异形  说着怪话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么你们长相都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,有的长着很多眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:15.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,有的拥有蛇一样的鳞片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:18.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,多么恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们很是头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么人类这么难相处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:26.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,以貌取人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:29.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,明明很弱却很固执  动不动就生气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:33.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,最终这样的声音如波浪般散开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们与人类开始了战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:39.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是相当大的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:43.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,然后弱小的人类一瞬间就败北
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,不知何时便消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:53.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,就这样  我们迎来了没有人类的和平世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,这是起源的故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:59.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,以前还流行过搜寻残党  狩猎人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:02.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  当做宠物或者吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:05.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过怎么说也不存在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,现在住在这的就只有我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:14.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,你们今晚住哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,野营
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么说这也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:23.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,还有小孩子在  很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:27.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,我会给你介绍旅馆的  住在这个城镇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  这就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  要住在这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:33.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,住在这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:38.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,住在这！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,被窝软绵绵的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,虽然没有在这停留的预定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:57.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:58.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,探险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,难以理解的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,那个  我和爸爸留宿很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:07.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸不开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:11.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆没有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,不开心的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样接着旅行会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:21.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,能修好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:23.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:28.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸能修好  爸爸能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:29.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:32.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,安静点  别动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:57.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,只是个客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,我无法理解你因何愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,而且  我刚才也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,说到底哥雷姆没有感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:14.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是爸爸的身体都僵硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:16.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽都看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:20.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,你的发言是错误的见解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:22.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,你绝对慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:26.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,明天要早起  到就寝的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要  我还不想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:28.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,否决
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,否决你的否决
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,哇  角修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,别一直摸它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,有可能会又坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,谢谢爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:09.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,不用感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,今天去哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,补充消耗品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,买东西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:53.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:11.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,太廉价了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,之前的城镇出了两倍的价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:19.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过老板  这石头在这边儿可不是太稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,这点我觉得就合适了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,难以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,我希望给一个合适的价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:30.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,就算你这么说  这石头也就是这个样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:35.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:39.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,客人  这可是很贵重的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,眼睛  还是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,硅酸盐为主要成分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,非晶状物质
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:51.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,根据我的解析  这是赝品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:53.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,你哪来的依据
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:58.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆的眼睛能够看穿世间万物的构成物质
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:02.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,陈列的装饰品的金属部分不是纯金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:06.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,而是含有78%的劣质铜制品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,2%是金色的染色剂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,大多的宝石都是玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,剩下的都是劣质品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:18.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,也就是说  这家店的商品八成都是假货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:23.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,店主  你能推测出我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:38.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,拿了就赶紧滚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:42.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,不必多言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽  走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:51.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,又来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:22.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,喂  小猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:39.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:41.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,小猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,没事吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:49.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是小猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,觉得麻烦  本来是不想理你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,但你一直跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:59.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是因为我迷路了  我也睡不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:03.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,才没有迷路  只是在乱逛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以说你这叫迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:08.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:12.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,那些别管了  让我摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,说了不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是的  你是哪来的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,一个人跑到这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:27.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,感觉你身上有一股熟悉的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:30.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么形容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:35.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,十分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,赶紧从这里离开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:00.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:02.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:03.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,果然爸爸你会来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:12.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,回旅馆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:13.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:18.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:22.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,我说  刚才见着了那个带着小孩的哥雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:24.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,超级可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,你肯定干了什么坏事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:27.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:31.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,只是感觉那个小孩特别美味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,说了出来  他突然就
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:37.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,你居然连这么小的小孩儿都不放过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:40.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,说了不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,刚才还好赶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是被感知到是人类就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:57.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,小孩子这种生物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,在好奇感兴趣的事物面前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:03.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,有着无法乖乖地待着的倾向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:04.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:06.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:09.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,刚才是怎么知道索玛丽在哪儿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,观察了你的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,观察？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,每当索玛丽从我的身旁离开时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:20.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,都是被什么东西所吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:23.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,这种情感无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:26.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是观察和分析却是可行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:29.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为是第一次与人类小孩接触
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:32.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,需要多花一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:37.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是  之后的旅程要是再迷路了可是大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:41.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,以后禁止随便从我的身边离开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:43.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,这个得视场合和时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:46.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:50.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,观察了城镇的居民后发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,牵手这种行为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:59.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,防止单独行动是很有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:03.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,一只手握住就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:12.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:16.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:22.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:28.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  有蝶蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:30.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:34.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,确实是一种防止单独行动有效的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:38.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是也极大的限制了彼此的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:43.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,有必要研究出一种更高效率的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:45.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:48.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽觉得这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:51.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}並ぶ影の大きさ比べ笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比较着并排的影子相视而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}夕暮れを背に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}把夕阳甩在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}そっと風に乗せたのは　まだ小さな願い事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}乘风而去的是那小小的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}永遠とか　生命だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}什么是永远  什么是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何も分からずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我还一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}真っ直ぐな瞳で　見上げた横顔は眩しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}只知道当我抬头仰望你时  你的侧脸总是那么地闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}重ねた手に伝う温もりは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手牵着手传递的这份温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どんなときも愛をくれたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}无论何时都在给予我爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}溢れ出すこの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}这不断溢出的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}あなたに届く日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}直到传达到给你的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:32.72,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}交わした約束進もう  未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:32.72,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}向着共同许下的诺言和未来  前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:41.02,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)\blur6\pos(1588.8,1062)}野草与鬼的住处
